Verifying Your Plabooks:
------------------------

1. Check for syntax errors:

  # anisble-playbook -i hosts playbook.yml --syntax-check

2. To do a dry run:

  # anisble-playbook -i hosts playbook.yml --check

*** Doing a dry run of the playbook will not commit any change on the managed nodes.

3. To list the hosts of each play in the Playbook:

  # anisble-playbook -i hosts playbook.yml --list-hosts
